Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: exp

    2 exp: assignexp

    3 assignexp: lvalue ASSIGN assignexp
    4          | orexp

    5 orexp: orexp OR andexp
    6      | andexp

    7 andexp: andexp AND relexp
    8       | relexp

    9 relexp: addexp
   10       | addexp EQ addexp
   11       | addexp NEQ addexp
   12       | addexp LT addexp
   13       | addexp LE addexp
   14       | addexp GT addexp
   15       | addexp GE addexp

   16 addexp: addexp PLUS mulexp
   17       | addexp MINUS mulexp
   18       | mulexp

   19 mulexp: mulexp TIMES unaryexp
   20       | mulexp DIVIDE unaryexp
   21       | unaryexp

   22 unaryexp: MINUS unaryexp
   23         | atomexp

   24 atomexp: NIL
   25        | INT
   26        | STRING
   27        | BREAK
   28        | LPAREN explist_opt RPAREN
   29        | idexp
   30        | IF exp THEN exp
   31        | IF exp THEN exp ELSE exp
   32        | WHILE exp DO exp
   33        | FOR ID ASSIGN exp TO exp DO exp
   34        | LET decs_opt IN explist_opt END

   35 idexp: lvalue
   36      | ID LPAREN args_opt RPAREN
   37      | ID LBRACE recfields_opt RBRACE
   38      | ID LBRACK exp RBRACK OF exp

   39 lvalue: ID lvaluetail

   40 lvaluetail: /* empty */
   41           | DOT ID lvaluetail
   42           | LBRACK exp RBRACK lvaluetail

   43 explist_opt: /* empty */
   44            | explist

   45 explist: exp
   46        | explist SEMICOLON exp

   47 args_opt: /* empty */
   48         | args

   49 args: exp
   50     | args COMMA exp

   51 recfields_opt: /* empty */
   52              | recfields

   53 recfields: recfield
   54          | recfields COMMA recfield

   55 recfield: ID EQ exp

   56 decs_opt: /* empty */
   57         | decs

   58 decs: dec
   59     | decs dec

   60 dec: typedecs
   61    | vardec
   62    | fundecs

   63 typedecs: typedec
   64         | typedec typedecs

   65 fundecs: fundec
   66        | fundec fundecs

   67 typedec: TYPE ID EQ ty

   68 vardec: VAR ID ASSIGN exp
   69       | VAR ID COLON ID ASSIGN exp

   70 fundec: FUNCTION ID LPAREN tyfields_opt RPAREN EQ exp
   71       | FUNCTION ID LPAREN tyfields_opt RPAREN COLON ID EQ exp

   72 ty: ID
   73   | LBRACE tyfields_opt RBRACE
   74   | ARRAY OF ID

   75 tyfields_opt: /* empty */
   76             | tyfields

   77 tyfields: tyfield
   78         | tyfields COMMA tyfield

   79 tyfield: ID COLON ID


